GrowEasy AI CSV Importer

An AI-powered CSV import application built with Next.js, Express.js, Google Gemini AI, and Docker. The application allows users to upload CRM CSV files, preview the data, intelligently map fields using AI, and generate standardized CRM-ready records.

Features
Drag & Drop CSV Upload
CSV Preview with Search
AI-powered CRM Field Mapping using Google Gemini
Batch Processing for Large CSV Files
Interactive Dashboard UI
Import Summary
CRM Results Table
Progress Bar During Processing
Docker Support
Responsive Design
Modern UI with Tailwind CSS

Tech Stack

Frontend
Next.js 16
React 19
Tailwind CSS 4
Framer Motion
React Dropzone
PapaParse
Axios
React Hot Toast
React Icons

Backend
Node.js
Express.js
Multer
CSV Parser
Google Gemini AI
dotenv
CORS

DevOps
Docker
Docker Compose

